<p>We can help you grow your career whilst still having a life away from work. In 2018, we were recognised as an organisation that offers the best work-life balance to employees.</p>
<p>Your benefits include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Competitive starting salary of &pound;27,000*</li>
    <li>30 days annual leave, plus standard public holidays</li>
    <li>Free travel on our networks (Zones 1-9) with an Oyster card for you and one other member of your household</li>
    <li>Membership of our pension scheme</li>
    <li>75% reimbursement on the price of an annual travel ticket outside the TfL network- plus an interest-free loan to pay for it</li>
    <li>Optional private medical benefit</li>
    <li>A range of staff retail and leisure discounts</li>
    <li>Extensive volunteering opportunities</li>
</ul>
<p>* If you are applying for one of our <a href="/corporate/careers/graduate-scheme/placement-opportunities">placement opportunities</a>, you will receive a bursary in place of a salary to cover London living expenses.</p>
